TONG JEUNG, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 7296. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. June 6, 1935. Stephen M. White, of San Francisco, Cal., for appellant. H. H. McPike, U. S. Atty., of San Francisco, Cal.

Before WILBUR and MATHEWS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed and that a decree be filed and entered accordingly.
